quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,32,"Alla daalani Ibuliisa …ìaawo o ha…óitaade sujjangol Aadama: E ko ha…óu maa sujjidugol e Malaa'ika'en …ìen sujjir…ìe …óoftagol yamiroore Am?"
  15,33,"Ibuliisa jaabori townitaare: Sellantaa lam ka mi sujjanta …ìanndinke mo Tagu…óaa immorde e loopal yoorungal, …ìalewal waylotongal."
  15,34,"Alla daalani ibuliisa: Yaltu ka Aljanna, sabu ko a riiwaa…óo."
  15,35,"Pellet, kuddi e riiweede e yurmeende Am fawike e ma haa √ëalnde Darngal."
  15,36,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Joomi am, nennitanam hara A waraa-ni lam haa √±ande tagu gun immintinoytee."
  15,37,"Alla daalani mo: An on, ko a jeyaa…óo e nennitanaa…ìe laje mun …ìen."
  15,38,"Haa e √±alaande nde fow maayata nden si allaadu ndun wuttaama araunuru."
  15,39,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Joomi am, sabu ko majjinir…óaa mi kon, ma mi labinan …ìe geddi …óin ka leydi, ma mi majjin …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe e laawol focciingol ngol."
  15,40,"Si wanaa …ìen …ìe su…ìi…óaa e jeyaa…ìe Maa fii ko rewa Maa."
  15,41,"Alla daali: Ngol ko laawol fotondirngol, hewtinayngol ka Am."
  15,42,"Pellet, jeyaa…ìe Am la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen, a alanaa…ìe …ìen kattal, a hippataa kadi bewnugol …ìe, si wanaa …ìen jokku…ìe ma e majju…ìe …ìen."
  15,43,"Pellet Jahannama wonii fodoore Ibuliisa e …ìen jokku…ìe mo e majju…ìe …ìen fow."
  15,44,"Jahannama no mari dame jee…ói…ói ka …ìe naatirta, damal kala e majje no heertinanaa jokku…ìe Ibuliisa …ìen ka naadiree."
  15,45,"Pellet, hulu…ìe Joomi mun …ìen, …ìe …óoftii yamirooje Makko …ìe wo…ó…óitii e ha…óaa…ói Makko, …ìen wonii e aljannaaji e …ìulli."
  15,46,"∆Åe wi'anoyte tuma …ìe naatata: Naatiree …ói hisugol e kala √±awu, da…óoo…ìe e kala kulol."
  15,47,"Men itti kala ko woni e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe immorde e konnaagu e ngayngu. ∆Åe wonti musi…ó…ìe yi…óindir…ìe, joo…óoday…ìe e nda…ó…óule hi…ìe ndaarindira."
  15,48,"Tampere he…ìataa …ìe ton, …ìe wonaa kadi yaltintee …ìe ton. Ko …ìe duumotoo…ìe nder ton."
  15,49,"An Nulaa…óo, anndin jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen, wonnde ko Min woni Haforanoowo tuubu…óo e ma…ì…ìe, Hinnotoo…óo …ìe."
  15,50,"Anndinaa …ìe wonnde lepte Am …óen, ko …óen woni lepte muusu…óe …óen. Yo …ìe tuubu …ìe ruttoo e Am fii no Mi haforana …ìe, …ìe da…óa lepte Am."
  15,51,"Humpitaa …ìe kadi fii Malaa'ikaa…ìe ho…ì…ìe Annabi Ibraahiima …ìen addannoo…ìe mo welo-welo …ìi…ó…óo gorko e halkeede yim…ìe Luuti …ìen."